      "text": "Zero star , I would given to this bank , cause the customer service is sucked, never pick up the call & the relationship department also sucked , they treated their customer very rude, I call relationship departmen his name Jerry he said cause I can not connect to the customer service , I ask him to transfer me to the customer service , but what he do instead , he hung up my phone call after he said he has work to do. funny, he didn’t  think I have work to do too, i already waste my time just to call you, how come you guys can work in the relationship department with the attitude like that. very disappointed.",
